text: Haris Seferović (born 22 February 1992) is a Swiss football player. He plays as a striker for Emirati club Al Wasl and the Switzerland national team. == References == Category:1992 births Category:Swiss footballers Category:Association football forwards Category:2014 FIFA World Cup players Category:UEFA Euro 2016 players Category:2018 FIFA World Cup players Category:Living people Category:2022 FIFA World Cup players Category:Sportspeople from the canton of Lucerne
